metadata.name: BORED EH
metadata.description: Steezy Apes are the most steezed out, swagged out, tatted and heavily dripped out apes in the metaverse. The 444 Genesis pieces all feature hand-drawn elements that give each ape a custom look and feel. Inspired by streetwear and hip hop culture, all 444 Steezy Apes carry that vibe through and through. #LFG #SAGFAM
